---
import RootLayout from '../components/RootLayout.astro'
import GoToAppButton from '../components/GoToAppButton.astro'
---
<style>
  .page-content {
    max-width: min(1500px, 90%);
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .pricing-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .pricing-card {
    width: min(100%, 300px);
    box-shadow: 1px 1px 7px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    background: var(--card-bg);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 15px;
  }

  .pricing-card h2 {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  .center {
    text-align: center;
  }
</style>
<RootLayout title="Pricing - Feynote">
  <div class="page-content">
    <h1>Always Free</h1>

    <br />

    All features within FeyNote are <i>completely</i> free to use and it's our goal for this platform to be an accessible place without any ads or limits on amount of content.

    <br /><br />

    We <i>do</i> have some benefits for contributors (similar to a Patreon-like contributor model), those supporter tiers <i>only</i> increase limits on things that are exceedingly costly to host, such as extra-large file uploads.

    <br /><br />

    All funds that are contributed go directly towards the improvement of the platform, and our artists. We do not seek to make a profit from this app. If you find FeyNote useful, please consider supporting us!

    <br /><br />
    <br /><br />

    <div class="pricing-list">
      <div class="pricing-card">
        <h2>Free</h2>

        <div>
          All application functionality, for free.
        </div>

        <ul>
          <li>Unlimited documents</li>
          <li>Unlimited embedded images</li>
          <li>Unlimited devices</li>
          <li>Document revisions (up to 10)</li>
          <li>Content Importer</li>
          <li>Absolutely zero ads, ever</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="pricing-card">
        <h2>Quill Bearer</h2>

        <div>
          $2/mo or $20/yr
        </div>

        <ul>
          <li>High resolution images (2k)</li>
          <li>Larger embedded files (20MB)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="pricing-card">
        <h2>Inkling</h2>

        <div>
          $5/mo or $40/yr
        </div>

        <ul>
          <li>High resolution images (4k)</li>
          <li>Larger embedded files (50MB)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="pricing-card">
        <h2>Tome Keeper</h2>

        <div>
          $10/mo or $80/yr
        </div>

        <ul>
          <li>That's it - but thank you, we really appreciate it</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <br />
    <br />

    <div class="center">
      <GoToAppButton />
    </div>
  </div>
</RootLayout>
